Fireplace/reveal effects Pico project.

Default pins:
- GPIO 14: reset button to GND, using internal pull-up
- GPIO 15: PDLC smart film relay/driver input
- GPIO 16: smoke burst relay/driver input
- GPIO 17: fireplace puzzle solved input
- GPIO 18: electric lock relay/driver input

MQTT publish:
- escape/puzzle/fireplace/solved
- escape/post/cubby/4/state = ready or completed

MQTT commands:
- escape/pdlc/on
- escape/smoke/burst
- escape/lock/trigger
- escape/post/query
- escape/game/reset

When the local reset button is pressed, the Pico republishes its POST state.

Use relay, MOSFET, or isolated driver modules. Do not switch mains power directly from Pico hardware.
